<subSubSection id="C321653AD35CA0662DABF8C2FE694F42" pageId="9" pageNumber="43" type="distribution">
<paragraph id="8B8436B1D35CA0662DABF8C2FE694F42" blockId="9.[151,1436,1482,1959]" pageId="9" pageNumber="43">
<emphasis id="B94FEAA3D35CA0662DABF8C2FD314F29" bold="true" box="[198,359,1821,1847]" pageId="9" pageNumber="43">Distribution.</emphasis>
Widely distributed in Southern Ocean and associated boundary currents in Southern Hemisphere, between 
<number id="3DF32496D35CA0662CF1F89DFDEA4F42" box="[412,444,1858,1884]" pageId="9" pageNumber="43" value="20.0">20</number>
° and 
<number id="3DF32496D35CA0662C93F89DFE764F42" box="[510,544,1858,1884]" pageId="9" pageNumber="43" value="50.0">50</number>
°S.
</paragraph>
</subSubSection>
